    "en": {
      "title": "Gota can stay in Singapore only until the 29th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "International media reports that the government of the country has officially informed Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa that the former President Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa can stay in Singapore for a period of 15 days only.",
        "Accordingly, he will have to leave Singapore before the 29th. Mr. Gotabaya Rajapaksa left Sri Lanka due to public opposition due to the escalation of the crisis in Sri Lanka and he traveled first to the Maldives and then to Singapore."
      ],
